snippet: Sainey Touray had two goals, and Lucky Mkosana added another as the host Harrisburg City Islanders of the U.S.L. Pro Division upset the Red Bulls, 3-1, on Tuesday night in the fourth round of the Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup.
abstract: Harrisburg City Islanders of the USL Pro Division defeat New York Red Bulls, 3-1, in the fourth round of the Lamar Hunt US Open Cup.
lead_paragraph: Sainey Touray had two goals, and Lucky Mkosana added another as the host Harrisburg City Islanders of the U.S.L. Pro Division upset the Red Bulls, 3-1, on Tuesday night in the fourth round of the Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup.

headline.seo: Red Bulls Are Knocked Out of U.S. Open Cup
